        <div class="well">
          <h4>
            Tips
          </h4>
          <p>
            Integrate the social conversation around a Promoted Trend across media channels like TV, radio, website feeds and live events.
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/AbsoluteRadio" target="_blank" class="btn">Check out @AbsoluteRadio →</a>
          </p>
